---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="BrewLogica Privacy Policy - CoeCode" description="Privacy policy for BrewLogica - the AI-powered coffee logging app for serious home brewers.">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 pt-12 pb-16">
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
        <span class="text-[#FF5A5A]">BrewLogica</span> Privacy <span class="text-[#00DDEB]">Policy</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Your coffee data is yours. We're committed to protecting your privacy.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Privacy Content -->
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 p-8 mb-8">
        <p class="text-sm text-white/60 mb-6">Last updated: January 2025</p>

        <div class="space-y-8 text-white/80">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Our Commitment to Your Privacy</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              At CoeCode, we believe your brewing data is personal and should remain under your control.
              This privacy policy explains how BrewLogica collects, uses, and protects your information
              as you track your coffee journey.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Information We Collect</h2>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-[#FF5A5A]">Coffee and Brewing Data</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              BrewLogica stores information about your coffee beans and brewing sessions:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>Bean details (roaster, origin, process, variety, roast date)</li>
              <li>Bag information (weight, purchase date, price)</li>
              <li>Brew logs (method, parameters, ratings, notes)</li>
              <li>Photos of coffee bags and labels</li>
              <li>Grinder and equipment information</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-[#00DDEB]">Account Information</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>Email address (for account creation and login)</li>
              <li>Display name (optional)</li>
              <li>Subscription status</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-[#8A4AF3]">AI Feature Usage</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              When you use AI features, we process:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>Photos submitted for label parsing (processed by AI, not stored after extraction)</li>
              <li>Text submitted for brew parsing</li>
              <li>AI usage counts for subscription management</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-[#00FF7F]">Device and Usage Information</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Device type and iOS version</li>
              <li>App version</li>
              <li>Crash reports and performance data</li>
              <li>Anonymous usage analytics</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Core Features:</strong> Store and sync your beans, brews, and insights across devices</li>
              <li><strong>AI Features:</strong> Process photos and text to extract coffee information</li>
              <li><strong>Insights:</strong> Generate resting profiles and brewing analytics</li>
              <li><strong>App Improvement:</strong> Analyze anonymous usage to improve features</li>
              <li><strong>Support:</strong> Provide customer support and troubleshooting</li>
              <li><strong>Security:</strong> Protect against fraud and abuse</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Data Storage and Security</h2>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-[#FF5A5A]">Local Storage</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Your coffee data is stored locally on your device using SwiftData. The app works fully
              offlineâ€”you can log brews without an internet connection.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-[#00DDEB]">Cloud Sync</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              When you create an account, your data is securely synchronized using Supabase:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>End-to-end encryption in transit (TLS 1.3)</li>
              <li>Encrypted at rest in PostgreSQL database</li>
              <li>Row-level security ensures you only access your own data</li>
              <li>Regular security audits and backups</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-[#8A4AF3]">AI Processing</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Photos submitted for AI label parsing are:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Sent securely to our AI processing service</li>
              <li>Processed to extract text and coffee information</li>
              <li>Not stored after processing is complete</li>
              <li>Not used to train AI models</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Data Sharing and Third Parties</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              We do not sell your personal data. Limited sharing occurs only for:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Supabase:</strong> Cloud database and authentication (data storage)</li>
              <li><strong>Anthropic:</strong> AI processing for label and brew parsing</li>
              <li><strong>Apple:</strong> App Store subscriptions and payments</li>
              <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law or legal process</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Your Rights and Controls</h2>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-[#FF5A5A]">Data Access and Export</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>View all your data within the app</li>
              <li>Export your beans and brews (coming soon)</li>
              <li>Request a copy of all stored data</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-[#00DDEB]">Account Management</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>Delete your account and all associated data</li>
              <li>Use the app without an account (local-only mode)</li>
              <li>Manage subscription through App Store</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-[#8A4AF3]">AI Feature Control</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>AI features are opt-in (you choose when to use them)</li>
              <li>Manual entry always available as alternative</li>
              <li>View AI usage history in settings</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Data Retention</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Account data retained while your account is active</li>
              <li>Data deleted within 30 days of account deletion request</li>
              <li>Backups retained for 90 days for disaster recovery</li>
              <li>Anonymous analytics may be retained indefinitely</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              BrewLogica is intended for users 13 and older. We do not knowingly collect personal
              information from children under 13. If you believe a child has provided information
              to us, please contact us immediately.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">International Data Transfers</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Your data may be processed in the United States where our servers are located.
              We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place to protect your data according to
              applicable privacy laws.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              We may update this privacy policy to reflect changes in our practices. Significant
              changes will be communicated through the app. Your continued use of BrewLogica after
              changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us:
            </p>
            <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-4 border border-white/10">
              <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@coecode.io" class="text-[#FF5A5A] hover:text-[#E54848]">privacy@coecode.io</a></p>
              <p><strong>Support:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@coecode.io?subject=BrewLogica Privacy" class="text-[#00DDEB] hover:text-[#00B8C4]">support@coecode.io</a></p>
              <p><strong>Address:</strong> Coe Code LLC, Missoula, Montana, USA</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Navigation Links -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
      <a
        href="/brewlogica"
        class="px-6 py-3 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        Back to BrewLogica
      </a>
      <a
        href="/brewlogica/terms"
        class="px-6 py-3 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        Terms of Use
      </a>
      <a
        href="/connect"
        class="px-6 py-3 bg-[#FF5A5A] hover:bg-[#E54848] rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
